[A] China: National Health Commission, 83 693 total cases, 4634 deaths
Date: Mon 20 Jul 2020
Source: China National Health Commission [abridged, edited]
http://en.nhc.gov.cn/2020-07/21/c_81136.htm


On 20 Jul 2020 (as of midnight 21 Jul 2020):
- 11 new cases of confirmed infections (3 imported cases -- 2 in shanghai municipality, 1 in Sichuan province; 8 locally transmitted cases -- 7 in Xinjiang Uygur autonomous region, 1 in Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps); no new cases of suspected infections and no deaths.
- A total of 2015 imported cases have been reported.
- 83 693 confirmed cases and 4634 deaths; 78 817 recovered and discharged from hospital; 772 488 close contacts with infected patients; and 7108 are under medical observation.
- 6 new asymptomatic cases (including 1 imported); 1 asymptomatic, imported case confirmed as symptomatic; 149 asymptomatic cases under medical observation (including 80 imported cases).
- 1958 cases in Hong Kong [an increase of 73 cases since 19 Jul 2020], and 46 in Macau.

